2106 void free_messages()
2107 {
2108  int rc;
2109 
2110  rc = MB_Clear(b_interest_rate);
2111  #ifdef ERRCHECK
2112  if (rc != MB_SUCCESS)
2113  {
2114  fprintf(stderr, "ERROR: Could not clear 'interest_rate' board\n");
2115  switch(rc) {
2116  case MB_ERR_INVALID:
2117  fprintf(stderr, "\t reason: 'interest_rate' board is invalid\n");
2118  break;
2119  case MB_ERR_LOCKED:
2120  fprintf(stderr, "\t reason: 'interest_rate' board is locked\n");
2121  break;
2122  case MB_ERR_INTERNAL:
2123  fprintf(stderr, "\t reason: internal error. Recompile libmoard in debug mode for more info \n");
2124  break;
2125  default:
2126  fprintf(stderr, "\t MB_Clear returned error code: %d (see libmboard docs for details)\n", rc);
2127  break;
2128  }
2129 
2130 
2131  exit(rc);
2132  }

4547 FLAME_output * add_FLAME_output(FLAME_output ** outputs)
4548 {
4549  FLAME_output * current;
4550 
4551  current = (FLAME_output *)malloc(sizeof(FLAME_output));
4552  CHECK_POINTER(current);
4553  current->next = *outputs;
4554  *outputs = current;
4555 
4556  current->type = -1;
4557  current->format = -1;
4558  current->location = NULL;
4559  current->period = -1;
4560  current->phase = -1;
4561  current->flag = 0;
4562 
4563  return current;
4564 }
4565 
4566 void free_FLAME_outputs(FLAME_output ** outputs)
4567 {
4568  FLAME_output * current, * next;
4569 
4570  current = *outputs;
4571  while(current)
4572  {
4573  next = current->next;
4574  free(current->location);
4575  free(current);
4576  current = next;
4577  }
4578  *outputs = NULL;
4579 }
4580 
4581 /* add_location */
4587 void add_location(double point, location ** p_location)
4588 {
4589  location * current = *p_location;
4590  location * tmp = NULL;
4591  location * newlocation = NULL;
4592  int found = 0;
4593 
4594  while(found == 0)
4595  {
4596  if(current == NULL) found = 1;
4597  else if(point > current->point) found = 1;
4598  else
4599  {
4600  tmp = current;
4601  current = current->next;
4602  }
4603  }
4604 
4605  newlocation = (location *)malloc(sizeof(location));
4606  CHECK_POINTER(newlocation);
4607  if(tmp)
4608  {
4609  tmp->next = newlocation;
4610  }
4611  else
4612  {
4613  *p_location = newlocation;
4614  }
4615 
4616  newlocation->next = current;
4617  newlocation->point = point;
4618 }
4619 
4620 /* freelocations */
4625 void freelocations(location ** p_location)
4626 {
4627  location * head = *p_location;
4628  location * tmp = NULL;
4629 
4630  while(head)
4631  {
4632  tmp = head->next;
4633  free(head);
4634  head = tmp;
4635  }
4636 
4637  *p_location = NULL;
4638 }

5178 void free_firm_agent(xmachine_memory_firm_holder * tmp, xmachine_memory_firm_state * state)
5179 {
5180  if(tmp->prev == NULL) state->agents = tmp->next;
5181  else tmp->prev->next = tmp->next;
5182  if(tmp->next != NULL) tmp->next->prev = tmp->prev;
5183 
5184  free_int_array(&tmp->agent->employees);
5185  free_loan_static_array(tmp->agent->loan_list, 2);
5186 
5187 
5188  free(tmp->agent);
5189  free(tmp);
5190 }

5557 void transition_firm_agent(xmachine_memory_firm_holder * tmp, xmachine_memory_firm_state * from_state, xmachine_memory_firm_state * to_state)
5558 {
5559  if(tmp->prev == NULL) from_state->agents = tmp->next;
5560  else tmp->prev->next = tmp->next;
5561  if(tmp->next != NULL) tmp->next->prev = tmp->prev;
5562 
5563  add_firm_agent_internal(tmp->agent, to_state);
5564  free(tmp);
5565 }
5566 
5567 void add_firm_agent_internal(xmachine_memory_firm * agent, xmachine_memory_firm_state * state)
5568 {
5569  xmachine_memory_firm_holder * current = (xmachine_memory_firm_holder *)malloc(sizeof(xmachine_memory_firm_holder));
5570  CHECK_POINTER(current);
5571 
5572  current->next = state->agents;
5573  current->prev = NULL;
5574  state->agents = current;
5575  if(current->next != NULL) current->next->prev = current;
5576  current->agent = agent;
5577 
5578  state->count++;
5579 
5580 }

5620 void add_firm_agent(int id, int isconstructor, int day_of_month_to_act, int isinsolvent, int day_of_week_to_act, int_array * employees, double wage_offer, int no_employees, int vacancies, int employees_needed, int day_of_month_wages_paid, double labour_productivity, int production_current, int production_estimate, int production_plan, double unit_goods_price, int day_of_month_production_completed, double unit_house_price, double labour_productivity_construction, double capital_productivity_construction, double capital_construction, int projects[], double loans_interest_rate, double debt, int inventory, int sales, double revenue, double costs, double equity, double liquidity, double capital_goods, int hasloan, double liquidity_need, loan loan_list[], double delta_housing_price)
5621 {
5622  xmachine_memory_firm * current;
5623 
5624  current = init_firm_agent();
5625  /* new line added to handle dynamic agent creation*/
5626  current_xmachine_firm_next_state = firm_start_state;
5627  add_firm_agent_internal(current, current_xmachine_firm_next_state);
5628 
5629  current->id = id;
5630  current->isconstructor = isconstructor;
5631  current->day_of_month_to_act = day_of_month_to_act;
5632  current->isinsolvent = isinsolvent;
5633  current->day_of_week_to_act = day_of_week_to_act;
5634  copy_int_array(employees, &current->employees);
5635  current->wage_offer = wage_offer;
5636  current->no_employees = no_employees;
5637  current->vacancies = vacancies;
5638  current->employees_needed = employees_needed;
5639  current->day_of_month_wages_paid = day_of_month_wages_paid;
5640  current->labour_productivity = labour_productivity;
5641  current->production_current = production_current;
5642  current->production_estimate = production_estimate;
5643  current->production_plan = production_plan;
5644  current->unit_goods_price = unit_goods_price;
5645  current->day_of_month_production_completed = day_of_month_production_completed;
5646  current->unit_house_price = unit_house_price;
5647  current->labour_productivity_construction = labour_productivity_construction;
5648  current->capital_productivity_construction = capital_productivity_construction;
5649  current->capital_construction = capital_construction;
5650  memcpy(current->projects, projects, 13*sizeof(int));
5651  current->loans_interest_rate = loans_interest_rate;
5652  current->debt = debt;
5653  current->inventory = inventory;
5654  current->sales = sales;
5655  current->revenue = revenue;
5656  current->costs = costs;
5657  current->equity = equity;
5658  current->liquidity = liquidity;
5659  current->capital_goods = capital_goods;
5660  current->hasloan = hasloan;
5661  current->liquidity_need = liquidity_need;
5662  copy_loan_static_array(loan_list, current->loan_list, 2);
5663  current->delta_housing_price = delta_housing_price;
5664 }

6024 void transition_household_agent(xmachine_memory_household_holder * tmp, xmachine_memory_household_state * from_state, xmachine_memory_household_state * to_state)
6025 {
6026  if(tmp->prev == NULL) from_state->agents = tmp->next;
6027  else tmp->prev->next = tmp->next;
6028  if(tmp->next != NULL) tmp->next->prev = tmp->prev;
6029 
6030  add_household_agent_internal(tmp->agent, to_state);
6031  free(tmp);
6032 }
6033 
6034 void add_household_agent_internal(xmachine_memory_household * agent, xmachine_memory_household_state * state)
6035 {
6036  xmachine_memory_household_holder * current = (xmachine_memory_household_holder *)malloc(sizeof(xmachine_memory_household_holder));
6037  CHECK_POINTER(current);
6038 
6039  current->next = state->agents;
6040  current->prev = NULL;
6041  state->agents = current;
6042  if(current->next != NULL) current->next->prev = current;
6043  current->agent = agent;
6044 
6045  state->count++;
6046 
6047 }

6077 void add_household_agent(int id, int day_of_week_to_act, double weekly_consumption_budget, double consumption_budget, int my_employer_id, double wage, int day_of_month_to_act, int day_of_month_wage_recieved, double mortgages_interest_rate, double tax_rate, mortgage_array * mortgages_list, int bank_id, double mortgages, double housing_payment, double equity, double housing_price, int housing_units, int dividends, double liquidity, double fund_shares, int previous_wages[], int hmarket_role, double equity_ratio, double minimum_equity_ratio, double mortgage_costs[])
6078 {
6079  xmachine_memory_household * current;
6080 
6081  current = init_household_agent();
6082  /* new line added to handle dynamic agent creation*/
6083  current_xmachine_household_next_state = household_start_state;
6084  add_household_agent_internal(current, current_xmachine_household_next_state);
6085 
6086  current->id = id;
6087  current->day_of_week_to_act = day_of_week_to_act;
6088  current->weekly_consumption_budget = weekly_consumption_budget;
6089  current->consumption_budget = consumption_budget;
6090  current->my_employer_id = my_employer_id;
6091  current->wage = wage;
6092  current->day_of_month_to_act = day_of_month_to_act;
6093  current->day_of_month_wage_recieved = day_of_month_wage_recieved;
6094  current->mortgages_interest_rate = mortgages_interest_rate;
6095  current->tax_rate = tax_rate;
6096  copy_mortgage_array(mortgages_list, &current->mortgages_list);
6097  current->bank_id = bank_id;
6098  current->mortgages = mortgages;
6099  current->housing_payment = housing_payment;
6100  current->equity = equity;
6101  current->housing_price = housing_price;
6102  current->housing_units = housing_units;
6103  current->dividends = dividends;
6104  current->liquidity = liquidity;
6105  current->fund_shares = fund_shares;
6106  memcpy(current->previous_wages, previous_wages, 3*sizeof(int));
6107  current->hmarket_role = hmarket_role;
6108  current->equity_ratio = equity_ratio;
6109  current->minimum_equity_ratio = minimum_equity_ratio;
6110  memcpy(current->mortgage_costs, mortgage_costs, 3*sizeof(double));
6111 }

9043 void add_node(int node_id, double minx, double maxx, double miny, double maxy, double minz, double maxz)
9044 {
9045  node_information * current = *p_node_info;
9046  node_information * tmp = NULL;
9047 
9048  while(current)
9049  {
9050  tmp = current;
9051  current = current->next;
9052  }
9053 
9054  current = (node_information *)malloc(sizeof(node_information));
9055  CHECK_POINTER(current);
9056 
9057  if(tmp)
9058  {
9059  tmp->next = current;
9060  }
9061  else
9062  {
9063  *p_node_info = current;
9064  }
9065 
9066  current->next = NULL;
9067  current->node_id = node_id;
9068  current->agents_in_halo = 0;
9069  current->agent_total = 0;
9070  current->agents = NULL;
9071  current->interest_rate_messages = NULL;
9072  current->buy_messages = NULL;
9073  current->bought_messages = NULL;
9074  current->sell_messages = NULL;
9075  current->sold_messages = NULL;
9076  current->goods_transactions_summary_messages = NULL;
9077  current->fired_messages = NULL;
9078  current->vacancy_stage1_messages = NULL;
9079  current->job_application_stage2_messages = NULL;
9080  current->job_application_stage1_messages = NULL;
9081  current->job_match_stage1_messages = NULL;
9082  current->job_change_messages = NULL;
9083  current->vacancy_stage2_messages = NULL;
9084  current->job_match_stage2_messages = NULL;
9085  current->employment_status_messages = NULL;
9086  current->loan_request_1_messages = NULL;
9087  current->loan_request_2_messages = NULL;
9088  current->loan_acknowledge_1_messages = NULL;
9089  current->loan_acknowledge_2_messages = NULL;
9090  current->firm_net_profit_messages = NULL;
9091  current->household_share_messages = NULL;
9092  current->capital_tax_messages = NULL;
9093  current->labour_tax_messages = NULL;
9094  current->unemployment_benefit_messages = NULL;
9095  current->general_benefit_messages = NULL;
9096  current->tax_rate_messages = NULL;
9097  current->fund_request_messages = NULL;
9098  current->new_entrant_loan_messages = NULL;
9099  current->interest_on_loan_messages = NULL;
9100  current->loan_writeoff_messages = NULL;
9101  current->housing_price_messages = NULL;
9102  current->buy_housing_messages = NULL;
9103  current->sell_housing_messages = NULL;
9104  current->bought_housing_messages = NULL;
9105  current->sold_housing_messages = NULL;
9106  current->mortgaging_capacity_messages = NULL;
9107  current->mortgage_requests_messages = NULL;
9108  current->mortgage_payment_from_sale_messages = NULL;
9109  current->mortgage_payment_messages = NULL;
9110  current->mortgage_writeoff_messages = NULL;
9111  current->housing_transactions_summary_messages = NULL;
9112 
9113 
9114  current->partition_data[0] = minx;
9115  current->partition_data[1] = maxx;
9116  current->partition_data[2] = miny;
9117  current->partition_data[3] = maxy;
9118  current->partition_data[4] = minz;
9119  current->partition_data[5] = maxz;
9120 }

9125 void free_node_info()
9126 {
9127  node_information * tmp, * head;
9128  head = *p_node_info;
9129 
9130  while(head)
9131  {
9132  tmp = head->next;
9133  free(head);
9134  head = tmp;
9135  }
9136 
9137  *p_node_info = NULL;
9138 }

9144 void clean_up(int code)
9145 {

9177  {
9178  fprintf(stderr, "ERROR: Could not delete 'interest_rate' board\n");
9179  switch(rc) {

9181  fprintf(stderr, "\t reason: 'interest_rate' board has not been created?\n");

9184  fprintf(stderr, "\t reason: 'interest_rate' board is locked\n");

10460 void add_int(int_array * array, int new_int)
10461 {
10462  if((*array).size == (*array).total_size)
10463  {
10464  (*array).total_size = (int)((*array).total_size * ARRAY_GROWTH_RATE);
10465  (*array).array = (int *)realloc((*array).array, ((*array).total_size * sizeof(int)));
10466  }
10467  (*array).array[(*array).size] = new_int;
10468  (*array).size++;
10469 }

10481  {

10484  {

10486  }
10487  (*array).size--;
10488  }
10489 }
